<li>CTA: Center title, no description slot, no footer slot, &quot;Learn more&quot; secondary button auto-add. Responsively, image goes to left, title left-justified, &quot;Learn more&quot; button disappears but arrow stays. CURRENTLY CALLED: Business Entity Landing Page variant</li>
